<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="NTM4.9">
<l>koṇṭa kōlak kuṟaḷuru vāycceṉṟu</l>
<l>paṇṭu māvali taṉperu vēḷviyil</l>
<l>aṇṭa mumnila ṉumaṭi yoṉṟiṉāl</l>
<l>koṇṭa vaṉvaril kūṭiṭu kūṭalē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>O circle! [You] be joined if</l>
<l rend="indent">He who acquired the sky and the earth with one step</l>
<l rend="indent">at the great sacrifice of Mahābalin in former times,</l>
<l rend="indent">going [there] bearing the form of a Dwarf with adornments</l>
<l>comes.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
